OL,3,C"I'm not just angry. I'm broken by
OL,4,Cthis."
OL,6,FA survivor of the Manchester Arena
OL,7,Fbombing say he is not just 'angry' but
OL,8,F'broken' after the bomber's brother
OL,9,Fattacked three prison guards.
OL,11,FHashem Abedi, 28, who is being held in
OL,12,Fa high-security unit at HMP Frankland,
OL,13,Fattacked guards with hot oil and
OL,14,Fhomemade weapons on Saturday, 12 April.
OL,16,FIn an open letter to the Justice
OL,17,FSecretary Martin Hibbert says he is
OL,18,Ffurious that the pain of survivors is
OL,19,F"being so blatantly disrespected by
OL,20,Fyour inaction".
