OL,3,C"I'm not just angry. I'm broken by
OL,4,Cthis."
OL,6,FAbedi was jailed for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum 55 years in prison after being
OL,8,Fconvicted of murdering 22 people in
OL,9,Fthe 2017 attack carried out by his
OL,10,Fbrother, Salman.
OL,12,FThe letter comes after the families of
OL,13,Ffive victims of the Manchester Arena
OL,14,Fbombing wrote to the Justice Secretary
OL,15,Fto express their "disbelief,"
OL,16,Ffollowing the attack on the prison
OL,17,Fguards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
