OL,3,C"I'm not just angry. I'm broken by
OL,4,Cthis."
OL,6,FIn the letter Mr Hibbert said: "Let's
OL,7,Fcall this what it is: a catastrophic
OL,8,Ffailure of your duty to protect prison
OL,9,Fstaff and the public from an
OL,10,Funrepentant terrorist.
OL,12,F"Not only was Abedi allowed the
OL,13,Ffreedom to move around and use
OL,14,Ffacilities that should never be
OL,15,Favailable to someone like him ` he was
OL,16,Fable to track and target three prison
OL,17,Fguards using boiling oil and homemade
OL,18,Fweapons."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
