OL,6,F"I'm not just angry. I'm broken by
OL,7,Fthis. And I am furious that the pain
OL,8,Fof survivors like me is being so
OL,9,Fblatantly disrespected by your
OL,10,Finaction.
OL,12,F"This cannot continue. Something
OL,13,Fdrastic needs to be done. Not
OL,14,Ftomorrow. Not next month. Now.
OL,16,F"Review his prison privileges. Strip
OL,17,Fhim of any access to areas where he
OL,18,Fcan make or find weapons. Protect your
OL,19,Fstaff. Protect the memory of those we
OL,20,Flost. Respect those who survived.
