OL,3,C"I'm not just angry. I'm broken by
OL,4,Cthis."
OL,6,F"Because right now, it feels like
OL,7,Fyou've forgotten us."
OL,9,FThe father-of-one was left with a
OL,10,Fspinal cord injury and his daughter
OL,11,FEve suffered severe brain damage as a
OL,12,Fresult of the bombing.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Sir Keir Starmer says he is
OL,15,F"appalled" by the attack and promised
OL,16,Fthat the government will urgently
OL,17,Finvestigate what happened.
