OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's spokesman said:
OL,7,F"The Prime Minister is appalled by the
OL,8,Fattack that we saw at the weekend and
OL,9,Fhis thoughts are with the officers
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,F"Prison staff work around the clock to
OL,13,Fkeep the country safe and we will
OL,14,Fnever tolerate the violence that is
OL,15,Ftargeted towards them.
OL,17,F"It's clear that something went
OL,18,Fterribly wrong in the management of
OL,19,Fthis offender and the Government is
OL,20,Fcommitted to carrying out an
OL,21,Finvestigation to urgently get answers."
